$$\text{corr}(v_{\text{val}}) = \frac{1}{n} \sum_{i,j} \text{Cov}(v_{\text{val},i}, v_{\text{val},j}) = \frac{1}{n} \sum_{i,j} \left( v_{\text{val},i} - \bar{v}_{\text{val}} \right) \left( v_{\text{val},j} - \bar{v}_{\text{val}} \right)$$

